An IDE is the easiest, least error-prone way to develop, manage and deploy Java classes. It provides many
benefits to developers, including:
* increased productivity,
* code completion,
* refactoring of code,
* debugging tools,
* version control,
* and team development.

IntelliJ IDEA, is one of several, IDE's, available for Java. It is also written in Java, developed by JetBrains.
